Create an app.R file.
load shiny with library(shiny)
Add ui and server elements,
as well as shinyApp(ui = ui, server = server).
Click Run - Check it works.


library(shiny)
# UI -----
ui &lt;- fluidPage(
  h1("Hello, World!")
)

# Server -----
server &lt;- function(input, output, session) {
}

# Run the app -----
shinyApp(ui = ui, server = server)


